{"tid":1509950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一手資料！和你塞攻略 — 前機師爆料！","createTime":"2019-08-27T04:10:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T11:04:58.000Z","uid":306045,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b08bb7e7b76bb627ebd8dfba64c253cd940d7d24","tid":1509950,"uid":306045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:10:38.000Z","msg":"老老柒柒圍狗屋不如<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>日日圍國泰城</ins></span></span></strong>，同塞機場條路概念一樣，無人返到工就無機走到，原理同罷工無分別~~<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>1. 朝早多人圍就會影響一整日schedule</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n每朝早最多人番工時段係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>0700-0900</ins></strong></span></span>，一班機delay就會牽連同日嘅班次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nCX KA 講緊每日近百班機，仲要大部分係短途早機，來來回回好幾轉，飛完夜晚又要緊接住飛歐美加，只要朝早飛唔到就順帶下晝夜晚零晨機<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>冚家cancel/delay</ins></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之啲機返唔切，就無機走，所以一定要<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>朝早無人番到工</ins></span></span></strong>先可以影響到之後既schedule<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>2. 大大力挫貨運量</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n除咗客運量仲有貨運，只要停飛一日，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>佢既成本好撚大</ins></span></span></strong>，絕對唔係一個小數目，可想言之停飛兩日啲高層應該喊到收唔到聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n機場嘅春袋比起客運更多係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>貨運</ins></span></span></strong>，所以先咁緊張要申請禁制令呀~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3. 一定要塞大嶼山主要幹道！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n若然因航啲mon post狗收到風圍佢城絕對有權叫機組番機場report duty，對大公司黎講要喺機場set個office容乜易，但只要無人過到去都係無人番到工~~~ <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>兩邊齊攻想番工都難</ins></span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然因航無可能炒撚曬所有人，但始終佢地工會唔夠power去令所有人無後顧之憂去罷......<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只要佢地番唔到工公司都吹佢地唔脹，所以大家夠薑9月1-3日日入去圍因航和你塞啦！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f33e8f33023d168208dbed5751872bd38291c313","tid":1509950,"uid":286964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:10:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">求幫推</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最新post 睇得清楚d + 加左今天有義士再審係頂！</span></span>(極正經)(請推至長期置頂)被捕義士進程，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f839b2eb3e075e2b18c948eca2315647586ad04a","tid":1509950,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:11:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrh9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3