宣布罷工，立此民調望各位網友號召全港打工仔同老闆幫我個人罷工行動作一個決策參考！<br />\n升級罷工，全民自決，網民發起問卷調查！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508197\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508197</a><br />\n<br />\n👨🏻&zwj;🍳👨🏻&zwj;🏭👩🏻&zwj;🚒👩🏻&zwj;🔬👩🏼&zwj;🏫👷&zwj;♂👨🏼&zwj;🎤👨🏾&zwj;🔧👩🏻&zwj;💼👨🏻&zwj;💻<br />\n一分鐘 填一填｜ <br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSe-vNbJsdOviermmz3NGLPkXZN0GvOPKkkTrDb8QxaeS35C7w/viewform?vc=0&amp;c=0&amp;w=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSe-vNbJsdOviermmz3NGLPkXZN0GvOPKkkTrDb8QxaeS35C7w%2Fviewform%3Fvc%3D0%26c%3D0%26w%3D1&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrh9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=0b9853b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSe-vNbJsdOviermmz3NGLPkXZN0GvOPKkkTrDb8QxaeS35C7w/viewform?vc=0&amp;c=0&amp;w=1</a><br />\n<br />\n網民自發，全民參與，意見咨詢，決策參考。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KpD40fE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKpD40fE.jpg&h=6cea06ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5dCmh2k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5dCmh2k.jpg&h=274a80cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d285fc5693465050bab2643ace658c5392cba413","tid":1509950,"uid":306045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"67143ea2690181479ba9a87eb28cc49a7f5dd5c3","tid":1509950,"uid":170445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:16:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:18:42.000Z","msg":"今朝焦土之母又出黎放火，各位手足識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49909221f599e7edfc4dcae556dbf1ffc929c597","tid":1509950,"uid":59559,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:18:50.000Z","msg":"搞都搞大陸航空公司先啦"},{"pid":"6eef1b58a7294082f501f1eb5a341cdc8cd57e1a","tid":1509950,"uid":285367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:19:16.000Z","msg":"同埋機場咁多手足 分分鐘佢地自己塞自己話返唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f7d62ab06e54f2bb41f668ba980a11326cbe718","tid":1509950,"uid":25424,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8077ee797747adf475107141dd11a4a607ca3e4a","tid":1509950,"uid":196450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:17:30.000Z","msg":"又搞鳩國泰? 唔係話支持國泰咩?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:21:49.000Z","msg":"一向已經係仆街公司啦<br />\n成日都用唔同理由炒人，令樽水都話員工偷野，如果唔係公會點會成鳩日示威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係連登仔入世未深見所謂英資就盲撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"419dcec7b3d46bd698ee3546e7d7e3aa4172fa3b","tid":1509950,"uid":306045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8077ee797747adf475107141dd11a4a607ca3e4a","tid":1509950,"uid":196450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:17:30.000Z","msg":"又搞鳩國泰? 唔係話支持國泰咩?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:22:48.000Z","msg":"就係支持佢地先間接令佢地罷工呀~~~ <br />\n佢地主動罷就會俾人秋，好多因航之友都話佢地電話裝曬監視軟件，基本上所有黃絲嘅fb都清曬反送中content，同新疆無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe6a79fa73a065391f40cb9865620bb484c9339","tid":1509950,"uid":198990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:23:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da59a3fd75ff47a33522d2b59b7de2225b2a727c","tid":1509950,"uid":66649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:23:30.000Z","msg":"係都搞HKA啦"},{"pid":"664e88d5589604c0dbcbebcb7a779ce154a72321","tid":1509950,"uid":306045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49909221f599e7edfc4dcae556dbf1ffc929c597"